quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  38,17,"Muñño e kon ko ɓe wi'ata; annditaa jeyaaɗo Amen on, Daawuuda, jom doole. Ko o ɗuuɗunooɗo tuubugol"
  38,18,"Men eltii pelle ɗen, hiɗe subbunhinoda e makko, ka kiikiiɗe e ka weetugol"
  38,19,"e colli ɗin, hiɗi mooɓindiraa, kala e majji no tuubana Mo"
  38,20,"Men semmbini laamu makko ngun, Men yeɗi mo Annabaaku e fasinteegal"
  38,21,"Hara kumpital wenjunooɓe ɓen arii maa, nde ɓe ƴawunoo ka ganngunal"
  38,22,"Nde ɓe naatuoo ka Daawuuda, o ɗenƴii ɓe. Ɓe wi'i: \"Wata a hulu ! Ko wennjuɓe ɗiɗo; goɗɗo e amen tooñii oya. Ñaawir goonga hakkunde amen, wata a tooñu, tinndinaa men e laawol focciingol ngol"
  38,23,"Oo ko musiɗɗo am: himo jogii baali cappanɗe jeenay e jeenay, min miɗo jogii baalii gootii. O wi'i: \"Henndinam ngii\"; o foolimi e yewtere"
  38,24,"O maaki: \"Pellet, o tooñirii ma lamndagol baalii maa ngii, waɗtugol e baali makko ɗin\". Ɗuuɗii ko hawtuɓe tooñindirta hakkunde maɓɓe, si wanaa ɓen gomɗimɓe, ɓe golli moƴƴuɗi - ɓen non no fanɗi. - Daawuuda felliti, wonnde Men jarribike mo. O insinanii Joomi makko, o suuyiri sujjugol, o tuubi"
  38,25,"Men yaafanii mo ɗum. Pellet non, hino woodani mo ko Amen, ɓadal e moƴƴude ruttorde"
  38,26,"Ko an yo Daawuuda, Men waɗii ma lomto ka leydi. Ñaawir goonga hakkunde yimɓe ɓen, wata a jokku mbeleeɗe, sakko ɗe majjine e laawol Allah ngol\". Pellet, ɓen majjooɓe e laawol Allah ngol, hino woodani ɓe lepte tiiɗuɗe, sabu ko ɓe yejjitiri kon, Ñalaande hasboore nden"